{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter <strong>Hamster City</strong>, where every road and building fuels your food-gathering empire! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/Movie_016-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1738788261\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build infrastructure, unlock unique buildings, and watch your hamsters thrive as you climb the leaderboard to become the ultimate Chief!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/Movie_008-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1738788261\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build and Expand:</strong> Construct roads and add buildings to create a city that maximizes food gathering.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Level Up and Compete:</strong> Upgrade buildings to gain an edge and compete on the global leaderboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic City Planning:</strong> Each road, building, and upgrade can give you an advantage in gathering resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlockable Structures:</strong> Discover new buildings that add layers of strategy to your hamster-led empire.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Idler in the Background:</strong> Hamster City runs while you\u2019re away, letting you focus on other tasks and return to find your city thriving!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/Movie_010-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1738788261\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join us on our Discord to become beta testers!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738788261","background_raw":"https://share